WEBVTT

00:06:58.813 --> 00:07:02.546
And I got into this state
of soul-searching,

00:07:02.570 --> 00:07:06.175
trying to really discover my role

00:07:06.199 --> 00:07:09.228
as a psychiatrist in Africa.

00:07:09.252 --> 00:07:13.799
And after considerable consultation
and soul-searching,

00:07:13.823 --> 00:07:16.927
talking to colleagues, friends and family,

00:07:16.951 --> 00:07:19.082
it suddenly dawned on me

00:07:19.106 --> 00:07:24.243
that actually, one the most reliable
resources we have in Africa

00:07:24.892 --> 00:07:26.177
are grandmothers.

00:07:27.707 --> 00:07:29.273
Yes, grandmothers.

00:07:29.661 --> 00:07:30.904
And I thought,